column2: SELECT DISTINCT po.objid AS phot_id, tm.ra AS tmass_ra, tm.dec AS tmass_dec, tm.j AS tmass_mag_j, tm.jIvar AS tmass_ivar_j, tm.h AS tmass_mag_h, tm.hIvar AS tmass_ivar_h, tm.k AS tmass_mag_k, tm.kIvar AS tmass_ivar_k, tm.phQual AS tmass_quality INTO MyDB.XMC_full_#MASS FROM MyDB.XMC_full_pos tmp INNER JOIN PhotoPrimary po ON po.objid = tmp.objid INNER JOIN TwoMass tm ON tm.objid = po.objid ORDER BY phot_id
